    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Full version now ➡️ Rover_Mechanic_Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1753711733\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到火星</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Rover Mechanic Simulator》中， 玩家将扮演第一个火星殖民地的机械师。您的任务包括火星探测车的维修和维护，以便其余船员可以使用它们收集有关行星结构的详细信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在此免费版本的Rover Mechanic Simulator中，您将可以浏览游戏的整个教程，并在玩完整版之前学习有关维修和保养Mars Rovers所需的所有知识。 您从此游戏中保存的文件也将在完整版游戏中运行，所以请不要担心，玩得开心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用各种设备 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用许多设备把漫游车的最小部分拆卸。使用不同的工具，如螺丝刀，压缩机，烙铁，3D打印机等等。在游戏的后期阶段，您将能够升级您的设备，使您的工作更加愉快和有效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/c6050391258430773ecdcb7318529296.avif?t=1753711733\" width=610 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >维修PCB</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/0890202ae1b9d29446ee18d8a5dc23ce.poster.avif?t=1753711733\" width=610 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/0890202ae1b9d29446ee18d8a5dc23ce.webm?t=1753711733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些部件不需要全部更换。您可以使用特殊的工作台来恢复损坏的IC，并清洁和维护在流动站工作期间磨损的部件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >积累经验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/6af2b3b80ed20c191d001fdcd62f2952.poster.avif?t=1753711733\" width=610 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/6af2b3b80ed20c191d001fdcd62f2952.webm?t=1753711733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种装置，帮助你为火星探测器的维修过程做好准备。但是要小心，它的设计很娇气，草率的决定可以增加对一台脆弱科学仪器的损害，这将需要更多时间与资源来完成这项工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >修复火星车</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/ba7c653c1878aba1d5c7f33d639c2a11.poster.avif?t=1753711733\" width=610 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/ba7c653c1878aba1d5c7f33d639c2a11.webm?t=1753711733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在火星有许多以往服务人民的装置，不过在某一点它们坏了。你可以恢复它们服务。由于你的工作他们会繼續执行任务通过发送行星的专门信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >”勇气号火星探测器“， ”机遇号探测器”跟其他的探测器已经为人民服务了多年，由于你它们还可以！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1314160/extras/c6050391258430773ecdcb7318529296.avif?t=1753711733\" width=610 height=206 /></span></p>",
